fields.name: AssessmentActivityId
fields.description: The activity ID of the operation that produced this result.

fields.name: AvailablePatchCountByClassification
fields.description: Summarization of patches available for installation on the machine by classification.

fields.name: LastModifiedDateTime
fields.description: The UTC timestamp when the operation finished.

fields.name: OsType
fields.description: The operating system type of the machine.

fields.name: PatchServiceUsed
fields.description: Specifies the patch service used for the operation.

fields.name: RebootPending
fields.description: The overall reboot status of the VM. It will be true when partially installed patches require a reboot to complete installation but the reboot has not yet occurred.

fields.name: StartDateTime
fields.description: The UTC timestamp when the operation began.

fields.name: StartedBy
fields.description: Indicates if operation was triggered by user or by platform.

fields.name: Status
fields.description: The overall success or failure status of the operation. It remains "InProgress" until the operation completes. At that point it will become "Unknown", "Failed", "Succeeded", or "CompletedWithWarnings."
